OL,4,CViolence and abuse against shop workers
OL,5,Cincreasing, survey says
OL,6, Violence and abuse against shop workers
OL,7, is on the rise but the perpetrators are
OL,8, rarely prosecuted, new research finds.
OL,10,FThe retail trade body, the British
OL,11,FRetail Consortium (BRC), says there
OL,12,Fwere on average 455 incidents a day in
OL,13,F2019, up 7% on the previous year.
OL,15,FIt said things have worsened during the
OL,16,Fpandemic and called for greater legal
OL,17,Fprotections for retail workers.
OL,19,FThe government said it had advised
OL,20,Fcourts to increase sentences for
OL,21,Fviolence against frontline workers.
